{"tid":478322,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"立會流會　朱凱廸︰為阻惡法打仗","createTime":"2017-11-24T03:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T13:06:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f00b9e32a52f04780df07d09f92aa459dbb3a980","tid":478322,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:12:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171124/20224099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171124%2F20224099&d=5JUcXyOfbCuqnENuqF3TZ4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=fa3c65c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171124%2F20224099&h=4a5a1ffc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171124/20224099</a><br />\n<br />\n立會流會　朱凱廸︰為阻惡法打仗<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】為力阻建制派於明年3月補選前修改《議事規則》，泛民議員昨在立法會大會續會時，由朱凱廸和毛孟靜先後兩次要求點算法定人數，其中毛在開會不足一小時後，趁建制派「小休」離座，要求點算法定人數的一次，立法會鳴鐘逾15分鐘後，建制派仍有7名建制派議員未及趕返議事廳開會，最終令大會僅欠一人宣告流會，是10月新立法會年度以來第二次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171124/large/1123cwl1107.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171124%2Flarge%2F1123cwl1107.jpg&h=fee87a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n建制派小休離座後，有議員未及趕返議事廳開會，立會最終流會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廖長江︰40人點編更<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸會後指，希望告訴巿民，民主派正打一場持續幾個月的仗，目的是捍衞立法會《議事規則》不被建制派單方面更改，「係有幾條惡法，包括《國歌法》、一地兩檢，同現時吹風吹得好行的23條立法」，又指現時政府和建制派就是鋪排立法會通過修改《議事規則》後，惡法將逐條提交到立法會，「我哋𠵱家每一次開會，其實都係同緊呢啲惡法鬥爭。<br />\n<br />\n建制派「班長」廖長江流會後，被問到有否「編更」開會時，反指「點編更呀？我哋得40個建制派議員」，指法定開會門檻人數是35人，建制派「只有」40人是不可能編更，立法會主席梁君彥會後指，開會是每位議員的職責，亦受公眾監督，希望議員能盡責開會，未來不會再流會。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙"},{"pid":"351fac17b7b1f869154cdbd799dcf6fbbcf4708d","tid":478322,"uid":31,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:18:58.000Z","msg":"40人要搵35條友坐係度都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e3c17c32c1e7cef84b18d978e0f41e3dd09e27","tid":478322,"uid":47558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:20:00.000Z","msg":"heidi 雖然係左膠，但佢真係最撚勤力，泊埋白鴿黨 d 垃圾比較真係差幾班馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e692ce62c99e7c35b035fc0679ec5ccc925f544","tid":478322,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:29:40.000Z","msg":"有公共性非私怨可以po落時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家真係越來越少人關注立會"},{"pid":"9d29cf5684ccff7ab372a21a9438efa1e43477a5","tid":478322,"uid":12424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:41:05.000Z","msg":"好過鄭松泰"},{"pid":"d266bf9e372fd0807e47ad29885ac70efae7a9ed","tid":478322,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T12:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好過鄭松泰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢扮緊民主派架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過無人理佢之嘛"},{"pid":"e8124c9816c9b67f039565861b4fec91f8e2c5b9","tid":478322,"uid":135217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好過鄭松泰</blockquote><br />\n鄭蟲泰唔洗扮friend咩????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}